===Adjective===
'''dead'''

#not [[alive]]; [[lack]]ing [[life]].
#:''All of my grandparents are dead.''
#someone who is so [[hate]]d by another that they are absolutely [[ignore]]d by them.  ("''He is dead to me''")
#(''Of a computer or other electric appliance'') completely [[inactive]]: without [[power]].
#{{cricket}} describing the state of the [[ball]] when not in [[play]], and [[run]]s may not be [[score]]d and [[batsman|batsmen]] cannot be [[out]].
# {{baseball}} {{slang}} an 1800s baseball term meaning a player who is tagged out

